PrecisAuthority to enter into the Canada-Alberta-Northwest Territories NORTHERN RIVER BASINS STUDY Amending Agreement (No. 1) which extends the period for for completion of the technical study into the cumulative effects of industrial development on the ecology of northern rivers for one year (March 31, 1996) and will the management and coordination of the study and reduce its overall cost.
